formThreeBId.notesToCertificate: 1.We have relied upon the estimates given by the management in case of costs other than construction cost.Land is developed through obtaining development rights , the partners of the firm are owner of the land and since the land area which on which this scheme is constructed is for both the phases, Phase I & II. For Phase I BU was received prior to RERA. Development Right value for phase II has to be calculated proportionately and in absence of enough documents we have considered the same as provided by the management.The same is considered as per amount shown under "Advance for Land".The compliance with maintenance of RERA A/c is not validiated while issuing the certificate. This Certificate is for Wings G,H,I, J only. As informed to us the books of accounts are not seperately maintained for both the phases.as informed by the management that from F.Y.2016-17 expenses debited in Profit and Loss account are pertaining to Phase II only.Unit consideration and received amount for booking deposit is considered as given by management and amounts shown under the head Block G,H,I & J. Partner's loan in Indian Bank  has been transferred to books of the promoter. no of units released are reduced for arriving total units mortgaged for this certificate. promoter has taken loan from IDBI which has outstanding balance of Rs 44378916/- as on 31/07/2020 as per books of accounts, however promoter has not mortgaged any unit or the project land for this loan hence we have not shown it in the schedule. Partner has mortgaged his personal property for this loan.Unsecured loan figures are taken as per books of accounts provided by Promoter.The details mentioned in Annexure A such as carpet area, booking status, unit consideration, date of agreement to sale, encumbrance status, name, KYC and mobile numbers of allotees are as provided by the management.We do not take responsibility of the scrutiny of books of accounts, this certificate is prepared basis the data provided to us by the management. As on the date of certificate as informed to us by the management there was no unutilised material. Promoter has received BU Permission for the project on 03/09/2020 . In case of project finance the origional loan was taken from india bulls which was subsequently transferred to Dhani Loans and Services Limited while certifying earlier certificate we had certified outstanding amount at 22875178/- however while issuing this certificate the outstanding amount is shown as 24,057,708.99/-, as spoken to management due to covid and due to change in management they have not updated outstanding amount to the tune of 70lacs and due to which there is difference in the outstanding amount.we have taken the outstanding amount as provided by the repayment schedule of the Dhani Loans and Services Limited.
